That was the last time I ever spoke to him.

00:17:15.560 --> 00:17:16.540
That was the last time I ever spoke to him.

00:17:16.540 --> 00:17:16.960
Japanese passenger, Akiha Yukitaka...
That was the last time I ever spoke to him.

00:17:16.960 --> 00:17:17.350
Japanese passenger, Akiha Yukitaka...

00:17:18.810 --> 00:17:19.500
I sent a D-mail to change that past.

00:17:19.500 --> 00:17:21.430
We have your daughter. Ransom is 100 million yen. 
Take the Shinkansen.
I sent a D-mail to change that past.

00:17:22.290 --> 00:17:25.350
So he wasn't in the crash,

00:17:25.350 --> 00:17:29.640
and you never brought moe culture to Akiba.

00:17:30.210 --> 00:17:32.740
And Akiba remained an electronics market.

00:17:34.420 --> 00:17:36.180
I was happy.

00:17:37.570 --> 00:17:38.850
These ten years...

00:17:39.650 --> 00:17:41.310
Feyr... Rumiho...

00:17:41.310 --> 00:17:43.770
I'll send that D-mail.

00:17:44.970 --> 00:17:47.900
My dad died in an accident, ten years ago.

00:17:47.900 --> 00:17:49.310
That's what truly happened.

00:17:49.970 --> 00:17:52.230
These ten years have been a dream.

00:17:52.230 --> 00:17:53.970
After all this time with him,

00:17:53.970 --> 00:17:57.220
I know how much he loved me.

00:17:57.220 --> 00:17:59.790
And Mayushii is my friend!

00:18:00.280 --> 00:18:02.540
I can't be selfish.

00:18:03.930 --> 00:18:06.360
You're sure?

00:18:09.850 --> 00:18:11.220
No.

00:18:12.300 --> 00:18:13.930
I'm not!

00:18:14.820 --> 00:18:16.130
I remember

00:18:16.130 --> 00:18:19.230
what happened before the world line changed.

00:18:19.230 --> 00:18:23.270
But I remember what happened after, too!

00:18:25.550 --> 00:18:28.730
It's all mixed together...

00:18:29.270 --> 00:18:31.440
And I don't think I'll be able to tell

00:18:31.440 --> 00:18:33.420
which is real, for much longer.

00:18:37.850 --> 00:18:41.360
There may be another way...

00:18:41.360 --> 00:18:43.380
I know! I can ask Kurisu—

00:18:43.380 --> 00:18:46.370
No! I don't want to cause you trouble.

00:18:46.370 --> 00:18:48.520
You really are my prince.

00:18:50.110 --> 00:18:54.470
It's time for me to wake up from this dream.

00:18:54.470 --> 00:18:57.830
But let me have one thing...

00:19:03.910 --> 00:19:07.110
Can I cry a little?

00:19:08.700 --> 00:19:09.570
Yea.

00:19:25.700 --> 00:19:26.990
Feyris-san...

00:19:27.680 --> 00:19:30.230
Yeah, she accepted.

00:19:31.520 --> 00:19:32.440
Get ready.

00:19:33.940 --> 00:19:35.910
Here I am!

00:19:37.670 --> 00:19:39.590
What's wrong, Kyouma?

00:19:39.590 --> 00:19:41.300
You look down!

00:19:42.330 --> 00:19:46.720
The kidnapping was just a joke. 
I love you, Daddy. See you soon.

00:19:49.640 --> 00:19:51.020
By the way...

00:19:52.440 --> 00:19:54.360
If the world reverts to how it was,

00:19:54.360 --> 00:19:57.160
will all my memories vanish?

00:19:57.740 --> 00:20:01.310
Your memories are from before and after

00:20:01.310 --> 00:20:02.810
the world line changed, right?

00:20:03.220 --> 00:20:04.530
I'm sure you'll remember.

00:20:04.880 --> 00:20:06.230
Good...

00:20:07.460 --> 00:20:12.890
Feyris wouldn't want to forget 
her time with Kyouma.

00:20:13.950 --> 00:20:15.010
Thank you.

00:20:17.680 --> 00:20:19.670
It's ready, Okabe!

00:20:22.870 --> 00:20:25.060
Goodbye, Daddy.

00:20:39.570 --> 00:20:40.770
Kyouma!

00:20:43.030 --> 00:20:45.270
Have you seen my cell phone?

00:20:45.270 --> 00:20:46.090
Feyris...

00:20:46.090 --> 00:20:48.270
Mayushii says she doesn't know.

00:20:48.270 --> 00:20:50.740
So you're the only other person I can ask.

00:20:53.960 --> 00:20:56.390
Kyouma, did you see what's on it?

00:20:56.390 --> 00:20:58.060
If you did, forget it!

00:20:58.060 --> 00:21:01.030
It must remain forever sealed!

00:21:02.500 --> 00:21:05.070
Kyouma, why don't you say anything?

00:21:05.070 --> 00:21:08.000
Like, "What's the it?"

00:21:08.820 --> 00:21:09.900
Feyris...

00:21:10.790 --> 00:21:12.110
Hey! Hey!

00:21:12.110 --> 00:21:14.110
Get your hands off her!

00:21:14.110 --> 00:21:16.210
You're doing something perverted again, right?

00:21:16.210 --> 00:21:17.560
Okarin's so bold.

00:21:18.660 --> 00:21:22.080
Kyouma and Feyris fought a great darkness,

00:21:22.080 --> 00:21:23.600
as lovers together, in a past life!

00:21:23.600 --> 00:21:25.680
We're really close!

00:21:26.100 --> 00:21:28.270
You fight lots of people, don't you?

00:21:28.270 --> 00:21:32.510
Is Feyris-san another one like Okabe?

00:21:34.960 --> 00:21:36.040
I'm sorry.

00:21:48.360 --> 00:21:52.820
<i>The IBN 5100 wasn't at Yanabayashi Shrine.</i>

00:21:53.820 --> 00:21:57.560
<i>Ten years ago, Feyris gave it to the shrine.</i>

00:21:57.560 --> 00:21:59.520
<i>They said it was there until last year.</i>

00:22:03.730 --> 00:22:04.970
<i>Where...</i>

00:22:06.740 --> 00:22:07.760
<i>...did it go?</i>

00:22:08.305 --> 00:23:08.516
